{"tid":206700,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"三行及地盤入行討論","createTime":"2017-04-18T13:52:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T18:27:13.000Z","uid":80635,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"75a868d970696ed53241478613033853aebc0623","tid":206700,"uid":80635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T13:52:42.000Z","msg":"請問有無邊範入行前景好d?<br />\n<br />\n我心水就想做泥水 因為無論裝修同地盤都需要泥水佬 <br />\n<br />\n我依家就做緊裝修管工 但發覺我唔係咁適合份工 人工唔高 無限OT 24小時手機無限工作訊息不停響 <br />\n<br />\n我睇過建造業議會d課程 唔洗比學費 又有錢收 不過人工就差唔多去到最低工資 讀完表現得好 會有公司請你 有無師兄係過來人 指點下小弟或者大家討論下"},{"pid":"b68be9b474def693547880207dcd0fa13fd887e3","tid":206700,"uid":50865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T13:54:39.000Z","msg":"同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec4512ff1ab677b666183132566c84bd47a3c83f","tid":206700,"uid":60651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T13:55:31.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d732e881452aa9c0de345b88aff1fc9a3c06d0","tid":206700,"uid":80635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T03:44:17.000Z","msg":"岩岩已經報左建造業議會課程 等一個星期通知"},{"pid":"33761c7b3b89ff42795a231e29d91c8752115892","tid":206700,"uid":85431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T03:52:07.000Z","msg":"三行乜春都唔識其實點做管工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係其實做緊雜工自己唔知"},{"pid":"8fe52d464677ad9adb67e04764e5c0d17d5e18ab","tid":206700,"uid":6032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T03:56:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三行乜春都唔識其實點做管工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係其實做緊雜工自己唔知</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef7b47243b83406f08b131eada88e3d8d8d42910","tid":206700,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,